					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介", "Junnosuke"},
					"“You don’t need to be so tense. You’ve got the strongest man on earth as your husband.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"淳之介"},
					"“不用那么紧张也没关系啦。因为你的老公可是最强的男人啊。”",
